Use the standard library
This is how to sum_product of numbers:
   Remember that sum is 0
   Remember that product is 1
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in numbers
      Remember that sum is (sum of sum and x)
      Remember that product is (product of product and x)
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is [sum, product]
Now you know